Instruction for testing acssampGUI
-------------------------------------------------

1. compile acssamp both in src and test

2. prepare the CDB

cd <...>/acssamp/ws/test
mkdir -p  CDB/MACI/Containers/Container
cp ENVIRONMENTS/wsTat/Container.xml CDB/MACI/Containers/Container/Container.xml

3. start ACS

export ACS_CDB=<...>/acssamp/ws/test
acsStart
acsStartContainer -cpp Container

4. start acssampGUI

acsStartJava alma.acssampGUI.acssampPanel

5. exercise the panel:
 - press SAMPLE (a running graph should be displayed on the JChart)
 - press PAUSE
 - ecc

Using ObjExp it is possible to change the value of the brightness;
note that the panel (currently) does not scale automatically so limit the values between 0 and 1.


